         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Philadelphos to his dearest Philippos,g reeting. Join those who deliver to you my letter in reference to Heronas so that, after they have reduced him to obedience, you go with them as long as they shall measure the fields. I pray for your health, dearest.</ab>
         </div>
